{"tid":48672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3休班警疑酒後多手　與3女街頭群毆被捕","createTime":"2016-12-21T08:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T08:54:29.000Z","uid":62257,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"803526c295c48f1f09c85b1a3f9309433f08ad84","tid":48672,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:05:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161221/bkn-20161221141912246-1221_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161221%2Fbkn-20161221141912246-1221_00822_001.html&d=hJWVbOOBUG1PRdmMe5Ar%2BnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=099421b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161221/bkn-20161221141912246-1221_00822_001.html</a><br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=hJWVbOOBUG1PRdmMe5Ar%2BnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=06a058ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 警隊醜聞連環爆，繼觀塘警區爆出警司鹹豬手事件，旺角疑發生休班男警夜蒲買醉疑「多手」引發街頭群毆醜聞。據悉，4名休班警員隸屬毒品調查科探員，包括1名偵緝警長、3名偵緝警員，其中3人涉嫌在公眾地方打架被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，4名探員今凌晨到旺角一夜店蒲通宵，至3時半左右，各人酒意濃厚盡興落街。期間，3名90後女子經過，與4警並肩而行，其中1女突感臀部被人摸，向附近數名男子質問，其後發生爭執，並扭作一團，其他男女亦加入戰團。雙方打至近旺角道28號，有人見狀報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，得悉其中3人是休班警員，他們分別姓邱(40歲)、姓唐(31歲)及姓潘(33歲)，他們報稱手部和身體受到，3名同為22歲的女子則分別姓梁、姓周和姓陳，她們報稱手部和身體受傷，其中周女口部受傷。涉事6人被警方以涉嫌在公眾地方打架拘捕，全部送院治理。案件暫列在公眾地方打架，交由旺角警區重案組跟進。所有被捕人士正被扣查，待警方進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人重申，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n本月14日，據悉，觀塘警區助理指揮官(刑事)警司王啟忠在所屬警區舉辦的聖誕派對上，涉嫌對多名女警作疑似性騷擾行為，並疑對一名欲上前制止的男警施以襲擊，他先以「長腿」、「大波」及「着超短裙」等字眼形容在場女士，其後又對多名女警「上下其手」作疑似性騷擾行為，更出手襲擊其他警員，一眾男女同袍都不齒其行為，案件交由東九龍總區作內部調查。"},{"pid":"cef83ef23ab7dc0c38bb43a787222888cf44d39a","tid":48672,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2859ed86cd5970fac9a25d774ec6cdac96a2a996","tid":48672,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecddfb6073f04ab675a72dbd3632c22118d24a26","tid":48672,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"仲要打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721b2cb80b19cfda29e3b84a86a4cbe19fc8969c","tid":48672,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係示威者唔還拖先輸"},{"pid":"371c251a4ea57b9ac7544904ac2b3adce955d998","tid":48672,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲要打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係示威者唔還拖先輸</blockquote><br />\n如果還拖速龍變鼻涕蟲"},{"pid":"d23b84f20534a2188c761009a8bc07560b133e91","tid":48672,"uid":1410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"毒品調查科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰幾個90後女女大獲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a488eae1d4c25dcf80df27de28a9170038065bd4","tid":48672,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af40fed8f5e560810c9cd8e4aaa3e38e7838b021","tid":48672,"uid":51340,"like":0,"dislike":0,